These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, lilac, purple, grey
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, cabbage, pomegranate, raspberry
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, spanish, colombian, italian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, jazz, soul
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, ambersy, time-travel, epic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, lacrosse, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, snowmobile
 1. the person eating broccoli is between the person who likes amber and the person watching thriller movies##2
 2. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the person watching ambersy movies is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the spanish##1
 7. the fan of funk is between the person driving the bus and the person watching epic movies##2
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the canadian##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is the fan of electronic##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the person eating cabbage##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the colombian##1
12. the italian is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
13. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the italian##1
14. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Color      | purple        | grey     | lilac | amber      |
| Food          | pomegranate | cabbage    | broccoli      | raspberry  |
| Nationality         | spanish  | italian    | canadian       | colombian     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | soul       | funk          | electronic |
| Movie-Genre           | time-travel    | thriller | ambersy      | epic     |
| Sport         | badminton   | baseball   | lacrosse      | sailing    |
| Transport     | bike        | bus        | snowmobile    | jet-ski    |

