 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the fan of house is the person eating radish##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the indian##1
 8. the person eating cherry is the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person driving the airplane is the malaysian##1
10. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
11. the indian is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person eating blueberry is between the person driving the roller and the person eating cucumber##2
13. the fan of reggae is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
15. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
